Contributor: Hangrui Bi

Reimplemented the deprecated glPerspective to offer control over perspective, the code now compiles with the latest glut library.

Added visualization of Gaussian curvature.

Usage:
Run make to build the 32-bit statically linked version, assuming freeglut v3.0 located at ./freeglut.

